      <title>德意志银行称信贷看起来比国债更安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/credit-looks-safer-bet-than-us-treasuries-deutsche-bank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行私人银行部门表示，鉴于美国财政前景不佳且赤字预计还会进一步上升，美国投资级债券似乎比美国国债更具吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/credit-looks-safer-bet-than-us-treasuries-deutsche-bank-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
